    <name>Sioyek</name>
    <summary>PDF viewer</summary>
    <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
    <project_license>AGPL-3.0-only</project_license>
    <description>
        <p>
           Sioyek is a PDF viewer designed for reading research papers and technical books. Some of the features are shown below.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Quickly search and open any file you have previously interacted with using sioyek.</li>
            <li>Search and jump to table of contents entries.</li>
            <li>Jump to any referenced figure or bibliography item.</li>
            <li>Quickly jump back to where you were with marks.</li>
            <li>Bookmarks</li>
            <li>Highlight text using different kinds of highlight, you can search among all the highlights.</li>
            <li>Using portals, you can link the paragraph's location to the figure's location.</li>
            <li>Customize all key bindings and some UI elements.</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
